# How to make the local be exactly similar to the remote
git fetch origin
git reset --hard origin/v3 --> branch
git clean -fd --> remove untracked files


# How to merge
# 1) Make sure your local branches are up to date
git fetch origin

# 2) Switch to master (the branch that will RECEIVE the changes)
git checkout master

# 3) Update master from remote
git pull origin master

# 4) Merge v3 INTO master
git merge v3

# 5) Push updated master to remote
git push origin master


Use :wq to save and quite
